      <!--<h2 class="align-center">-->
      <!--<strong>Digitize any agreement as finite state machine</strong>-->
      <!--</h2>-->
      <!--<p class="subtitle-1 align-center">-->
      <!--A-->
      <!--<strong>Live Contract</strong> is an agreement that is formalized as Finite State Machine ("FSM"). We-->
      <!--believe this-->
      <!--method is superior to formalizing an agreement in a natural language (-->
      <!--<em>paper contracts</em>) or in a programming language (-->
      <!--<em>smart contracts-->
      <!--</em>). An FSM may be represented as a simple flowchart. This makes it easily-->
      <!--<strong>understandable by both humans and computers</strong>. Using Live Contracts is great for-->
      <!--<strong>organizations and governments</strong>, as it allows automate procedures, simplify communication and-->
      <!--reduce-->
      <!--costs. It's also great for-->
      <!--<strong>consumers and citizens</strong> as it makes them self-reliant, rather than having to choose between-->
      <!--relying-->
      <!--on lawyers or blindly trusting organizations and governments.-->
      <!--</p>-->
      <!--<p class="align-center">-->
      <!--<a href="https://medium.com/@livecontracts/live-contracts-bringing-justice-through-blockchain-b06696386cf4"-->
      <!--target="_blank"-->
      <!--class="sr-button button-medium read-more-button button-1 circled">-->
      <!--Read more-->
      <!--</a>-->
      <!--</p>-->
      <!--</div>-->
      <!--<div class="spacer-big"></div>-->
      <!--</div>-->
      <div class="purpleSection row-section text-light">
        <div class="wrapper clearfix">
          <div class="column one-third">
              <div class="align-center">
                <img style="width:80px" src="img/independence.png" alt="Independence">
                <h5 class="testimonial-name">Independência</h5>
                <div class="testimonial-content">
                  Permitimos que as pessoas participem do sistema legal sem depender de advogados,
                  organizações fechadas ou governos.
                </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column one-third testimonial">
            <div class="align-center">
              <img style="width:80px" src="img/efficiency.png" alt="Efficiency">
              <h5 class="testimonial-name">Eficiência</h5>
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                LiveContratcts permite a automação de acordos e entendimentos legais sem necessidade de
                fornecer controle total à máquina
              </div>
            </div>
